@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zvbrto(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.05 - v0 + 0.49)) / (wp.sin(tmp + 0.17) - (tmp + 0.34 / v1 + 0.28)))
    v2 = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.15) / (v2 + 0.74 + tmp + 0.59)) - wp.cos(v2))
    v0 = wp.sin(v1)
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.sin(0.76))
    v1 = 0.74
    data[tid] = v0
